    "name": "Vengeance of Mr. Peppermint",
    "steam_appid": 2287560,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287560/extras/0834568a57ada607976dcd6604a9316b.avif?t=1734718583\" width=600 height=86 /></span><br>薄荷先生的复仇是一款硬核横向卷轴格斗游戏，灵感来自于经典的韩国犯罪影片。作为冷酷无情的薄荷先生侦探，你的工作就是找出下达命令和实施血腥报复的那个人。这一路上，你将看到无数罪犯正在侵扰这个被邪教毒害的城市。你可以决定用任何东西摧毁他们。但是，当你穿过堆积如山的尸体，擦拭薄荷先生整洁的西装上的血渍时，请小心，这位侦探最大的敌人可能是他自己。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287560/extras/609fda1c77c5aeea9fe503306fe893cc.avif?t=1734718583\" width=600 height=86 /></span><br><br>很久以前，一个杀手抓走了当地一名警察的孩子。这个女孩被杀害了，但她的哥哥却奇迹般逃了出来。二十年后，他像他的父亲一样，成为了一名侦探，他相信法律和秩序是构建社会的基础。但他的悲伤和痛苦把他推向了疯狂的边缘，他凝视深渊，逐渐清醒：现在，他必须找出并惩罚杀害他妹妹的凶手，不管有多少人挡在他的面前。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287560/extras/a9ba3eb103b4b49304a0a571ea99b101.poster.avif?t=1734718583\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287560/extras/a9ba3eb103b4b49304a0a571ea99b101.webm?t=1734718583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287560/extras/a9ba3eb103b4b49304a0a571ea99b101.mp4?t=1734718583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287560/extras/b3b38b7b413bb639e0f1445967fe2416.avif?t=1734718583\" width=600 height=86 /></span><br><br>薄荷先生对复仇的执念让他变成了杀人机器。通过精准操控打出连击，摧毁任何阻拦你的人，残酷地杀死他们。拼凑武器，把敌人射成红色血雾，或者抓住他们并利用环境消灭他们：钩子、肉类加工机、烤炉……可以使用任何东西残忍地终结打手们的犯罪生涯。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287560/extras/c0415b214795c0c1384c7be776da8b0e.poster.avif?t=1734718583\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287560/extras/c0415b214795c0c1384c7be776da8b0e.webm?t=1734718583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287560/extras/c0415b214795c0c1384c7be776da8b0e.mp4?t=1734718583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287560/extras/ea741d20b698ae943c37b2432833cc30.avif?t=1734718583\" width=600 height=86 /></span><br><br>复仇的执念伤害了薄荷先生。他越深入复仇，精神就越崩溃。他越残忍，故事就越变态。悖论出现了。无法回答的问题出现了。随着薄荷先生的复仇逐渐失控……到底谁才是真正的杀手？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287560/extras/201c7bb10c8d65b9ccace06d21938763.poster.avif?t=1734718583\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287560/extras/201c7bb10c8d65b9ccace06d21938763.webm?t=1734718583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287560/extras/201c7bb10c8d65b9ccace06d21938763.mp4?t=1734718583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
